<p>Click here for our <a href="/Forms/YMinistry/CampRegistration.pdf">registration form</a>.  This must be completed and sent into us along with your "Early Bird" payment or camp deposit.</p>
<p>For those NOT participating in our "Early Bird" rate program: A non-refundable deposit of  $150.00 is due by <b>April 15th</b> (installment payment plans may be arranged).  The remainder of the balance is due by <b>May 15th</b>.  All campers must have a deposit in order to reserve a space at camp.  NO SPACES will be reserved without a deposit!!</p>
<p>A registration packet will be sent out upon receipt of your child's application, including directions, a contract for camper conduct, and the health form.  <b>**Every camper must have a completed health form filled out and signed by a physician and a physical exam prior to the start of camp, Campers will not be allowed to attend camp without a health form.  Campers without completed health forms will be sent home!</b></p>

<p>A 10% discount will be offered for families with more than one child attending camp.  Campers referring NEW campers who attend a camp session will receive a $10.00 discount from their camp fee.  <b>***campers may receive either the 10% sibling discount OR the $10 finders fee, not both.</b></p>

<p>Scholarship applications are available through the camp office.  The amount of scholarship aid is determined by need.  Individual parishes are encouraged to raise funds to assist their young people in attending camp.</p>

<p>Transportation to and from camp may be arranged.  Please indicate on the application if you will be in need transportation assistance.</p>

